title: Nailing Picture Frames Outside
itunes:title: Nailing Picture Frames Outside
description:
Anthony and Gregg talk about toxic masculinity and the build up to Anthony's new special releasing. The guys discuss whether women should be involved in sports and how to properly kill a UFC fighter. Is posting about your ex-girlfriend on instagram a bad thing to do?
